<p><br /></p>

<h3 id="using-data-dashboards-in-emergency-response">Using Data Dashboards in Emergency Response</h3>

<p>Marko Mijic, Acting CHHS Deputy Secretary, explains how bringing data together, streamlining data management processes, and mapping data with a dashboard helped to support timely decision-making and response to California wildfires.</p>

